Package: asciiwright
Type: Package
Title: ASCII Wright Maps in R
Version: 0.13.0
Author: Codex Assistant [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Codex Assistant <codex@example.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Codex",
      family = "Assistant",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "codex@example.com"
    )
  )
Description: Creates Winsteps-inspired Wright maps as fixed-width ASCII text.
    The package aligns person and item locations on a shared latent-variable
    axis and annotates means and standard deviations in a text layout that
    works well in terminals, reports, and plain-text outputs.
